description:
We had a chance to go hands-on with the upcoming MSI Claw 8 Ai+ Lunar Lake powered handheld gaming PC, and so far, it's looking very promising! Powered by an Intel Core Ultra 200V CPU and backed by superfast LPDDR5X @ 8533MHz and the all-new Intel® Arc™ Graphics 140V with 8 Xe2 cores, this 8" 120Hz handheld might be worth it.

Key features:
Intel Core Ultra 200V CPU
LPDDR5X @ 8533MHz memory
Intel® Arc™ Graphics 140V with 8 Xe2 cores
8" 120Hz display
Compact and portable design

Powerful performance
Excellent battery life
Comfortable to hold
High-quality display
